ReadMe Group 16 Arduino 

1. Download the program to the Arduino controller
2. connect the controller to a voltage of five volts or USB hub.
3. Place the controller in a room filled with light
4. The lcd should display the righting “Good Morning”.
5. Turn of the lights or cover the photoresistor with your hand – the lcd should display the righting “Good Night”, the servo motor should begin operating, the led should be on and the buzzer should play a sound. 
6. Turn the light back on - all of the actions in 5. should stop and lcd displays "Good Morning".